tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Yenko is out of Yanmar x Rudolph and was produced right here in June of 2022.  His pedigree is special as he is Yanmar bred to a Party Monster daughter.  Yenko is standard colors but does carry pied.  He is health tested clear for  CMR1, PRA-cord1, DM, HUU and JHC.  Yenko is practically a clone of his daddy and we have high expectations for this amazing little guy! After his first show debut in the fall of 2022, Yenko earned his champion status before even reaching 9 months old.  We will continue showing him and try for his grand champion title next.  Yenko is now open for stud to approved females and is proven.



Stud Fee: 2K



DNA: ayay DD EmEm NS kyky

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Kaz
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Texas Top Notch Kaz the Wanderlust was produced here back in January of 2019.  Kaz is full littermate sister to Kofi and 1/2 sister to Cartel, Peavy and Tonga. She has one of the very best personalities and is practically perfect in conformation.  Kaz is built like a male and has produced some super nice off spring such as our very own Kayda and Astra.  This girl is a blue fawn that carries both cocoa and cream.  



DNA: aya dd Coco EMe nn kyky

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Peavy
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Texas Top Notch Blinding Lights aka Peavy was produced here back in September of 2019.  Peavy is 1/2 sister to Cartel, Tonga and Kaz; all sharing the same mom. She is a small girl with great substance and structure as well as a very sweet demeanor and eagerness to please.  Peavy is blue and tan and carries both cocoa and cream.  This girl is health tested clear of JHC, HUU, PRA-Cord1, CMR1 and Cystinuria 3. She produced a beautiful litter with our boy, Thunder Cat and was then bred to Narco for her second breeding and produced our amazing boy, Kamikaze and our girl, Pita. Peavy will most likely be bred again in late 2023 to one of our studs.



DNA: atat dd Coco EMe nn kyky

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Kayda
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Texas Top Notch Hardest to Love aka Kayda was produced here back in June of 2020.  She is a very well built female like her beautiful mom, Kaz.  Kayda is a solid cocoa that carries both chocolate and blue.  She is a super short, thick girl w/ an amazing personality just like her mom. Kayda is mom to Paper Trail, Bread Winner, Cash Money and Dirty Money.    







DNA: aa coco Bb Dd EME kyky

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Rudolph
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Texas Top Notch Life of the Party aka Rudolph was produced here back in October of 2020.  She is line bred out of our boy, Party Monster and our now retired, Trilogy.  Rudolph is a very petite girl that has very nice structure, great headpiece, and the most amazing temperment.  She produced an amazing litter w/ Yanmar in June of 2022 which resulted in our boy, ABKC CH Yenko and our girl, Yuli. She will be bred again in the fall of 2023



DNA: ayay DD EMEM nn kyky

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: ABKC Champion Yuki
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Texas Top Notch CH Yuki was produced here back in October of 2020.  She is a Yanmar daughter and that is very obvious looking at her build and characteristics.  This girl is 1/2 sister to Odyn, Yakka, Yenko and Yuli. Yuki is extremely muscular and has very nice conformation and movement.   She is health tested clear of JHC, HUU and CMR1. Yuki earned her ABKC Champion title in April of 2023 after her show debut in late 2022.  She will be bred in the fall of 2023.







DNA: ayay DD EMEM NS kyky

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Yakka
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Bully B Bulldogs Yakka of Texas Top Notch was co-produced w/ breeder Brittany Bell in November of 2020 and  is out of Yanmar and her beautiful girl, Gigi.  She is 1/2 sister to both Odyn , Yuli, Yenko and Yuki. Yakka is a very small girl and has great substance and structure.  She is health tested clear of JHC, HUU, DM, PRA-Cord1, CMR1 and Cystinuria 3. This girl will most likely be bred in 2023 to one of our studs.



DNA: ayay DD EMe NS kyky

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Tonga
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Texas Top Notch Heartless Valentine aka Tonga was produced here back on Valentine's Day of 2021.  She is full littermate sister to Cartel and 1/2 sister Kofi, Kaz and Peavy; all 4 being out of Taja.  Tonga is a very athletic, well built girl who is super smart.  She is a harlequin merle that carries both cocoa and blue.  This girl is health tested clear of JHC, HUU DM, PRA_Cord1, CMR1 and Cystinuria 3. Tonga was bred to Malakai and that pairing produced our beautiful chocolate merle girl, Toka.  She will most likely be bred again in the fall of 2023.



DNA: aa Dd Coco EME nn kyky Mm269

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Astra
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Texas Top Notch Lilac Astra was produced here back in March of 2021 out of Kaz and 908s Own Type R.   She is 1/2 sister to Kayda. Astra is a very small, correct female who loves to be the center of attention.  This girl is health tested clear of JHC, HUU, DM, CMR1 and Cystinuria 3. She produced an amazing litter with Odyn in the fall of 2023.







DNA: ata dd coco EME nn kyky

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Dirty Money
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Dirty Money was produced right here and is out of our very own, Kayda, and an outside male named Hush Money.  Dirty is littermate sister to Cash Money, Breadwinner and Paper Trail. This girl has the exact same DNA as her mom but also carries pied.  Dirty is health tested clear of JHC, HUU, PRA_Cord1, CMR1 and Cystinuria 3. She will most likely be bred to CH Yenko in late 2023.



DNA: aa coco Bb Dd EMEM NS kyky

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Vida
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
This extremely tiny girl was imported along with her brother, Beef,  from Hungary in April of 2022 from Small Heroes Kennel.  She is standard colors only and super tiny.  Vida is health tested clear of JHC, DM, HUU, PRA-Cord1, and CMR1. This girl is super athletic and very compact with excellent structure.  We plan to take her to  Odyn in 2023.  



DNA: ayay DD EmEm nn kyky

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Yuli
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Yuli was produced right here in June of 2022 out of Yanmar x Rudolph.  She and her brother Yenko are very special to us as they are out of Yanmar bred to a Party Monster daughter, putting both of our amazing boys together in one pedigree,  Yuli is standard colors but does carry pied.  She is health tested clear of  JHC, DM, HUU, PRA-Cord1, CMR1 and Cystinuria 3. We have big plans for this beautiful little girl!



DNA: ayay DD EmEm NS kyky

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Toka
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Texas Top Notch After Hours Toka was produced here in July of 2022 out of Malakai and Tonga. Toka is an aa chocolate merle girl that carries both blue and cream.  She is health tested clear of JHC, DM, HUU, PRA_Cord1, CMR1 and Cystinuria 3. We are thinking of pairing her with either Bread Winner or Paper Trail depending on how she develops when she is of age.  



DNA: aa coco Dd Ee nn kyky Mm268

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Nika
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Nika was the 2nd female French Bullog we added to our program back in 2015.  She was imported from Lithuania and is the main backbone to all of our color dogs today.  Nika is mom to Taja, who is mom, grandma and great grandma to most all of our color dogs we have currently.  Nika has since been retired and is living out her days with her wonderful owner Claire in Texas.



DNA: aya Dd EMEM nn kyky

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Nola
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Nola was the very first French Bulldog female we introduced to start our program back in 2015.  She was imported from Lithuania and produced many nice dogs over the years; several can be seen on our Production Page.  Nola has since retired and is living out her days being loved and spoiled by Stephanie and family in Texas.



DNA: ayay DD EMEM NS kyky

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Toki
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Toki was the 3rd female French Bulldog we added to our growing program back in 2015,  She traveled to us all the way from Hungary as a 4 month old pup.  This girl is the backbone of our standard dogs here today.  



DNA: ayay DD EME NS kyky

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Trilogy
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Texas Top Notch Trill aka Trilogy was produced right here back in 2017 and is out of now retired dogs Ecko and Toki.  This girl is super small and compact with the most sweet, comical personality.  She is mother to our dogs Odyn and Rudolph as well as several others on our Produced Page.  Trilogy and her mom are both retired  now and are living out their lives together spoiled rotten with a family in Michigan.



DNA: ayay DD EMEM nn kbrky

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Taja
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Texas Top Notch Beauty Behind the Madness aka Taja was produced right here back in 2017 and is out of our girl Nika and an outside stud named Cruz.  This girl really left her mark here being the mom, grandma and great grandma to several of our dogs today.  Taja seemed to outproduce herself with each and every breeding.  This beautiful girl is now retired and spoiled rotten with her wonderful owner Victoria in Texas.



DNA: ata dd Coco EMEM nn kyky

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Pita
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Pita is out of Narco and our girl, Peavy.  She is full littermate sister to our boy, Kamikaze. Pita is exactly why we did this breeding as she is small, compact and correct with the most beautiful face and great bone.  She is health tested clear of JHC, DM, HUU, PRA-Cord1, CMR1 and Cystinuria 3. Her personality is the absolute best as she loves to be held and loves attention.  Pita should be a great asset to our program in the future.



DNA: atat dd coco EMe nn kyky

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Aspen
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Aspen was produced here in September of 2022 and he is out of Thunder Cat x Kaz.  This beautiful boy is a maskless chocolate fawn that carries tan points, blue and cream.  Aspen is health tested clear of JHC, DM, HUU, PRA-Cord1, CMR1 and Cystinuria 3.  We are excited to see how this handsome guy matures and look forward to incorporating him into our breeding program. He is currently open for stud.



Stud Fee:  2K



DNA: ayat coco Dd Ee nn kyky

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Kamikaze
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Kamikaze is our stunning lilac and tan merle boy that was produced right here out of Narco x Peavy in Decemeber of 2022.  He is full littermate brother to our girl, Pita.  Kaze is a lilac and tan merle that carries cream.  He has excellent structure and we are planning to start showing him once he hits 6 months old.  Kamikaze is health tested clear of CMR1, PRA-cord1, HUU, JHC and Cystinuria 3.  He is open for stud.



                                                                        Stud Fee: 2K



DNA: ata dd coco EMe nn kyky Mm268

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Neva
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Neva is a beautiful little cream girl that is off Odyn and Scarlett (owned by a friend) and was born in February of 2023.  She is an amazing little girl with phenomenal structure, great bone and a beautiful head piece.  Neva is health tested clear of JHC, DM, HUU, PRA-Cord1, CMR1 and Cystinuria 3.  We have big plans for this perfect little girl and hope to get her into the show ring later this year as well



DNA: aya DD ee NS kyky

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Pyper
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Pyper Rose is a beautiful fawn color carrier that we produced in December of 2021 out of Kaz x Griffin owned by Tasha Chasteen.  This girl puts alot of males to shame with her huge head and rope, crazy thick substance and bone.  Pyper is a fawn that carries blue, cocoa, cream and tan points. She is health tested clear of JHC, HUU, DM, PRA-Cord1, CMR1 and Cystinuria 3. Pyper was bred to Cash Money for her first breeding and we are looking forward to seeing those puppies grow and mature.







DNA: ayat Dd Coco EMe nn kyky

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Louie
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Louie is an amazing chocolate and tan male covered in cream sired by our male, Malakai and grandsired by our boy, Kofi.  Louie is a solid, structurally correct male with great bone, a huge head and a compact body with no tail.  He is a very nice representation of the breed with a super sweet, laid back temperament to boot.  Louie is health panel clear of JHC, HUU, CMR1, DM.  His C3 and PRA-CRD1 testing is pending. 







Stud Fee: 2K



                                                                            DNA: ata DD coco ee nn kyky

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: High Roller
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
This stunning guy was produced right here in August of 2023 and is out of Cash Money x Pyper Rose.  He is an amazing looking young stud with the dna to match!  He is a lilac and tan that carries cream and testable. Roller is health tested clear of JHC, DM, HUU, PRA-Cord1,  CMR1 and Cystinuria 3.  We are excited to watch this beautiful boy mature and have big plans for him in our program.  We hope to have him open for stud in the summer of 2024.







                                                             



DNA: ata dd coco Bb eme nn kyky

tp/v1/dogs/females.title: Bunny
tp/v1/dogs/females.description:
Bunny was born on September 11, 2023.  She is out of The Breadwinner x Sassy (Griffin x Kaz). This beautiful girl is staying super short but has crazy bone and substance for a female.  Bunny is health tested clear of JHC, DM, HUU, PRA-Cord1, CMR1 and Cystinuria 3.  We have big plans for this beautiful girl.







DNA: ata Coco Bb Dd emem nn kyky
